'''巴尼斯紐約'''（英語：'''Barneys New York'''）是一家美國奢侈品連鎖[[百貨公司|百貨公司]]，總部位於[[紐約市|紐約市]]，共有三家旗艦店，分別位於紐約市、[[比佛利山莊|比佛利山莊]]和[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]，在美國其他城市也有較小的百貨店。該公司由巴尼·普利斯曼（Barney Pressman）成立於1923年的[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]。2019年8月，它宣布破产。正宗品牌集团（Authentic Brands Group）在2019年11月将其买下，并将“巴尼斯纽约”商标授予[[萨克斯第五大道|萨克斯第五大道]]<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2019/11/01/business/media/barneys-bankruptcy-authentic-brands.html Barneys Is Sold for Scrap, Ending an Era] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/11/01/business/media/barneys-bankruptcy-authentic-brands.html |date=20191105150030 }} Vanessa Friedman and Sapna Maheshwari, ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'', November 1, 2019</ref><ref>[https://fortune.com/2019/11/01/bankrupt-barneys-new-york-saks-fifth-avenue/ Barneys New York bankrupt] {{Wayback|url=https://fortune.com/2019/11/01/bankrupt-barneys-new-york-saks-fifth-avenue/ |date=20211117210007 }} Phil Wahba, ''Fortune'', November 1, 2019</ref>。

==巴尼斯紐約CO-OP==
巴尼斯紐約CO-OP創始于1986年，其商品售價較爲低廉，面向年輕的消費者<ref>{{cite web | url=http://vmsd.com/content/barneys-ny-ending-co-op-brand | title=Barneys N.Y. Ending Co-op Brand | publisher=VMSD.com | accessdate=2017-11-24 | archive-date=2016-10-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161012043928/http://vmsd.com/content/barneys-ny-ending-co-op-brand | dead-url=no }}</ref>。但在2013年巴尼斯紐約宣佈放棄CO-OP店，其中一部分的CO-OP轉爲正式的巴尼斯紐約商店。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/lydiadishman/2013/03/06/barneys-rebranding-co-op-stores-signals-the-start-of-a-more-luxe-era/#449bdb3a3240 | title=Barneys Rebranding Co-op Stores Signals the Start of a More Luxe Era | publisher=Forbes | date=6 March 2013 | author=Lydia Dishman | accessdate=2017-11-24 | archive-date=2017-12-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201045350/https://www.forbes.com/sites/lydiadishman/2013/03/06/barneys-rebranding-co-op-stores-signals-the-start-of-a-more-luxe-era/#449bdb3a3240 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

